name: The Magical Item #2: Arnab: The Ocean of Desires
description: In Zirafa, Dino learned many hidden techniques of teleportation, one of them was through a speaker gifted by Pikoz. He played his favorite track while lying on the open fields of Tatil. He found himself sailing in Arnab, the second magical location. Unlocking this portal will increase your Comfort Attribute by 330 MP (magical points) to remind you to take a break from time to time.
